Detailed Description

template<class NumberStar, class LargeNumber>
class InterpolateSketch< NumberStar, LargeNumber >

Functor class to determine normalized value given raw data point and the vector of sketch values for that chip and average values for all sketches.

See also: Sketch Quantile Normalization
